OL,3,CCouriers march into Royal Mail building
OL,5,FAnila Dhami went along to the protest
OL,6,Fto speak to some of the attendees.
OL,8,FCouriers in London stormed a Royal
OL,9,FMail building as part of a strike to
OL,10,Fdemand workers' rights including
OL,11,Fholiday pay and pensions
OL,13,FNearly 100 gathered in Whitechapel
OL,14,Foutside the headquarters of eCourier
OL,15,Fwhich is owned by Royal Mail.
OL,17,FThe work of these drivers includes
OL,18,Fmedical items such as blood and other
OL,19,Fmedical specimens.
