OL,5,F"So when your loved one has a major
OL,6,Fhemorrhage in a hospital, these guys
OL,7,Fare responsible for asking bags of
OL,8,Fbloods to keep them alive. Quite
OL,9,Foften, these guys are making less than
OL,10,Fminimum wage when doing that job,"
OL,11,Fexplained Alex Marshall, president of
OL,12,Fthe Independent Workers Union of Great
OL,13,FBritain.
OL,15,F"What we're arguing is just like Uber
OL,16,Fdrivers, Bolt drivers, recently, they
OL,17,Fshould be getting holiday pay and
OL,18,Fpensions.
