OL,3,CCouriers march into Royal Mail building
OL,5,F"Some of these guys have been working
OL,6,Ffor eCourier for over a decade, and
OL,7,Ffor that whole time they've never been
OL,8,Fgiven holiday pay for that whole time
OL,9,Fthey've never been given a pay rise,
OL,10,Fso their pay has essentially gone
OL,11,Fdown."
OL,13,FThe protestors demands include
OL,14,Fcompensation in the form of back-dated
OL,15,Fholiday pay, union recognition, a pay
OL,16,Fpackage of #20-an-hour plus mileage.
OL,18,FThe couriers got into formation to
OL,19,Fmark their strike.
