OL,3,CCouriers march into Royal Mail building
OL,5,FThe protestors were joined by
OL,6,Fsupporters including an A&E doctor
OL,7,Ffrom Newham Hospital.
OL,9,FHe said: "Couriers who provide this
OL,10,Fessential service, they are key
OL,11,Fworkers for the NHS and for our
OL,12,Fcountry are treated abysmally by their
OL,13,Fsub contractor as well as NHS
OL,14,Femployees.
OL,16,F"I'm here to support them in their
OL,17,Ffight for fair pay, dignity and
OL,18,Frespect in the workplace."
