OL,5,FKay Ballard from Unite, Tower Hamlets,
OL,6,Fadded: "They're asking for dignity,
OL,7,Fand wages that are owed (to) them.
OL,9,F"These eCouriers literally shift
OL,10,Fmedical, they keep hospitals going,
OL,11,Fthey're keeping every one of us
OL,12,Falive....would these managers work
OL,13,Fwith these wages? On these terms and
OL,14,Fconditions?"
