OL,5,F"We haven't had any complaints or
OL,6,Fclaims from individual drivers that
OL,7,Fsupport IWGB's position or the
OL,8,Fallegations made. eCourier offers
OL,9,Fcouriers the choice of being engaged
OL,10,Feither as workers (with entitlement to
OL,11,Frights such as holiday pay and sick
OL,12,Fpay) or as self-employed contractors,
OL,13,Fand notes that most have preferred to
OL,14,Fengage via the independent contractor
OL,15,Farrangement. We are currently in the
OL,16,Fprocess of reminding eligible couriers
OL,17,Fof the option to engage as workers."
